descriptionHTML:
Fives is a Unique way to tell the tell, using Circles that will count out the time.
The outside 12 circles is a break down of the seconds in the minute.
The next 12 circles will tell you the minutes within the hour.
Finally the 12 inside circles will tell you the hour itself.

Configuration options will allow you to modify
★ 12/24 hour, Battery, Date, 12 hour with Date and 24 Hour with Date
★ Text Color and Circle Color
★ Circle Color 2
★ Background Color

All colors have been taken from Google's Material Design Palette, so you can have a color scheme to match you device.

If you find any bugs, or would like to recommend any modification, please email the developer directly, requests made from within the comments will not be action-ed.

Please note, settings can only be accessed by the Android Wear App on your phone/tablet.

NOTE: Please make sure your watch is running Android Wear 5+. This will not work otherwise.

To install please refer to the Wear Support Page.
https://support.google.com/androidwear/answer/6140435

Is compatible with Android Wear 5+ devices

If you find any bugs, or would like to recommend any modification, please email the developer directly, requests made from within the comments will not be action-ed.

Please note, settings can only be accessed by the Android Wear App on your phone/tablet.
